Comment:
Recent experiences of working with other teams across abcam have been challenging to say it mildly.

- HR experience during recruitment of a new team member, which was a struggle from start to finish and was undermined and disrupted every step of the way, culminating in a salary offer that was massively below other recent hires for similar roles. This whole situation has been stressful and miserable, and feels like it was being actively sabotaged for reasons unknown;

- IT/digital where getting a new equipment set up in the lab seems to be almost impossible and feels as if any little progress we manage to make is met with new hurdles and obstacles that need to be conquered. Even though individual team members have been fairly responsive, those efforts don't equate to progress and positive outcomes and the whole experience has been frustrating and unnecessarily difficult.
